description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:10:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>军政府向缅甸叛乱分子学习，建立新的中国无人机舰队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/learning-myanmars-rebels-junta-builds-new-chinese-drone-fleet-2024-06-13/</link><description>去年，缅甸抵抗战士依靠分散的无人机舰队与东南亚最令人畏惧的军队之一进行战斗，取得了决定性突破。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 02:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/learning-myanmars-rebels-junta-builds-new-chinese-drone-fleet-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>陷入困境的七国集团领导人在意大利峰会上关注乌克兰战争和中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/troubled-g7-leaders-focus-ukraine-war-china-italian-summit-2024-06-13/</link><description>七国集团（G7）领导人周四开始年度峰会，寻求加倍支持乌克兰与俄罗斯的战争，并团结一致对抗中国的政治和经济野心。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 01:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/troubled-g7-leaders-focus-ukraine-war-china-italian-summit-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>美元因美国通胀降温而下跌，日元在日本央行之前脆弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-slips-cooler-us-inflation-yen-fragile-ahead-boj-2024-06-13/</link><description>由于美国通胀低于预期，主要货币兑美元周四保持涨势，但日元除外，日元在日本央行会议之前仍受到挤压，因美国政策制定者暗示利率将在一段时间内保持高位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 00:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-slips-cooler-us-inflation-yen-fragile-ahead-boj-2024-06-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促欧盟扭转电动汽车关税的“错误方向”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-eu-will-reconsider-ev-tariffs-state-media-reports-2024-06-13/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，北京希望欧盟重新考虑对中国电动汽车的关税，并停止在“错误的方向”上进一步发展，以保护其汽车行业免受竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 00:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-eu-will-reconsider-ev-tariffs-state-media-reports-2024-06-13/</guid></item><i